high mortality rate. Is this a new event (such as an outbreak of an unknown
disease with a high mortality rate), or is it an ongoing problem with a high
nosocomial infection rate associated with a high mortality rate (more likely
to be bacterial in origin than viral as stated in the above report)? -Mod.
